data.description: Villages of Berry Creek - This amazing home backs up to the greenbelt with beautiful views and even some deer that can be seen just past the fence line!  The backyard is a gardener's paradise, and the back patio is a perfect setting for relaxation and the morning cup of coffee!  With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms this updated home has been well maintained to include a brand-new built-in microwave and a complete whole home soft wash to preserve the beauty of the limestone. With the perfect location, this home is a quick drive to Austin, Tesla, Fort Cav or really anywhere you want to go!  Located just off 195 it has easy access to I35 and 130!  Make your appointment to see this home today!
